  m_text: "You are trying to get a specific power output \nfrom three power sources
    to three power sinks. \n\nYou can press the labeled button on each power \nsource
    to route power to the power sinks.\n\nPower routed from one source will always
    be split evenly.\n\nMatch all three power outputs to solve the puzzle."
